"},{"d":"सहस्राक्षश्च","m":"Indra of thousand eyes"},{"d":"जलेश्वरः","m":"god of waters"},{"d":"वरुणश्च","m":"Varuna"},{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"glorious"},{"d":"महादेवः","m":"MahaDeva"},{"d":"सर्वस्य","m":"all"},{"d":"लोकस्य","m":"worlds"},{"d":"कर्ता","m":"creator"},{"d":"ब्रह्मविदाम्","m":"creators"},{"d":"ब्रह्मा","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"एते","m":"all those"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"समागम्य","m":"reached"},{"d":"सूर्यसन्निभैः","m":"closely resembling the sun in radiance"},{"d":"विमानैः","m":"aerial car"},{"d":"लङ्कांनगरीम्","m":"to Lanka city"},{"d":"आगम्य","m":"having reached"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"अभिजग्मुः","m":"went towards"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"ततःसहस्ताभरणान्प्रगृह्यविपुलान्भुजान् ।अब्रुवंस्त्रिदशश्रेष्ठाराघवंप्राञ्जलिंस्थितम्","trans":"Then foremost of gods adorned with ornaments in hands lifted up their long shoulders and greeted Raghava with joined palms and spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"त्रिदशश्रेष्ठाः","m":"foremost of gods"},{"d":"सहस्ताभरणान्","m":"adorned with ornaments in hands"},{"d":"विपुलान्","m":"long"},{"d":"भुजान्","m":"shoulders"},{"d":"प्रगृह्य","m":"taking up"},{"d":"प्राञ्जलिम्","m":"greeted with both palms"},{"d":"स्थितम्","m":"stood"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"अब्रुवन्","m":"spoke as follows"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"कर्तासर्वस्यलोकस्यश्रेष्ठोज्ञानवतांप्रभुः ।उपेक्षसेकथंसीतांपतन्तींहव्यवाहने कथंदेवगणश्रेष्ठमात्मानंनावबुद्ध्यसे ।","trans":"\"You are the creator of the entire world, knowledgeable and the foremost Lord of the host of gods. How did you keep watching Sita falling into fire'?","words":[{"d":"सर्वस्य","m":"all sides"},{"d":"लोकस्य","m":"in the world"},{"d":"कर्ता","m":"creator"},{"d":"ज्ञानवताम्","m":"knowledgeable"},{"d":"श्रेष्ठः","m":"foremost"},{"d":"प्रभुः","m":"Lord"},{"d":"हव्यवाहने","m":"fire"},{"d":"पतन्तीम्","m":"falling"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"कथम्","m":"how"},{"d":"उपेक्षसे","m":"looking"},{"d":"देवगणश्रेष्ठम्","m":"foremost of the hosts of Devas"},{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"कथम्","m":"how"},{"d":"नावबुद्ध्यसे","m":"not know?"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"ऋतधामावसुःपूर्वंवसूनां च प्रजापतिः त्रयाणामपिलोकानामादिकर्तास्वयंप्रभुः ।","trans":"\" Among the Vasus, you are the Rtadhama and the creator of the three worlds and the first creator and selfconstituted ruler.\"","words":[{"d":"पूर्वम्","m":"in the past"},{"d":"वसूनाम्","m":"Vasus"},{"d":"ऋतधामा","m":"Rtadhama"},{"d":"वसुः","m":"Vasu"},{"d":"त्रयाणामपि","m":"creator of the three worlds"},{"d":"लोकानाम्","m":"in the world"},{"d":"आदिकर्ता","m":"first creator"},{"d":"स्वयंप्रभुः","m":"Lord himself"},{"d":"प्रजापतिः","m":"selfconstituted ruler"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"रुद्राणामष्टमोरुद्रस्साध्यानामपिपञ्चमः अश्विनौचापिकर्णौतेसूर्यचन्द्रामसौदृशौ ।","trans":"\"You are the eighth among the Rudras, fifth among the Sadhyas, two Aswins are your ears, and the sun and moon are your eyes.\"","words":[{"d":"रुद्राणाम्","m":"Rudra"},{"d":"अष्टम:","m":"eighth"},{"d":"रुद्रः","m":"Rudra"},{"d":"साध्यानाम् अपि","m":"among Sadhayas"},{"d":"पञ्चमः","m":"fifth"},{"d":"अश्विनौ","m":"twin Aswins"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"कर्णौ","m":"ears"},{"d":"सूर्याचन्द्रमसौ","m":"sun and moon are"},{"d":"दृशौ","m":"your eyes"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"अन्तेचादौ च लोकानांदृश्यसे च परन्तप उपेक्षसे च वैदेहींमानुषःप्राकृतोयथा ।","trans":"\"O Tormentor of enemies! You are at the beginning and at the end of the world. You are looking like a common man would look at Sita, when she was falling into pyre.\"","words":[{"d":"परन्तप","m":"tormentor of enemies"},{"d":"लोकानाम्","m":"in the world"},{"d":"आदौ","m":"at the beginning"},{"d":"अन्ते च","m":"and at the end"},{"d":"दृश्यसे","m":"seen"},{"d":"प्राकृतः","m":"common"},{"d":"मानुषोयथा","m":"like the man"},{"d":"वैदेहीम्","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"उपेक्षसे च","m":"looking as if you are ignorant"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"इत्युक्तोलोकपालैस्तैस्स्वामीलोकस्यराघवः अब्रवीत्त्रिदशश्रेष्ठान्रामधर्मभृतांवरः ।","trans":"Rama the upholder of dharma and foremost and supreme god spoke after the ruler of the world had spoken to him.","words":[{"d":"लोकपालैः","m":"ruler of the world"},{"d":"इति","m":"this"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having said"},{"d":"लोकस्य","m":"world"},{"d":"स्वामी","m":"Lord"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"धर्मभृताम्","m":"upholder of Dharma"},{"d":"वरः","m":"foremost"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"त्रिदशश्रेष्ठान्","m":"supreme god"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"आत्मानंमानुषंमन्येरामंदशरथात्मजम् सोऽहंयस्ययतश्चाहंभगववंस्तद्भ्रवीतुमे ।","trans":"\"I am Dasharatha's son, a human and thinking to be Rama. Tell me O divine creator, from where and whence I am here.\"","words":[{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"I am"},{"d":"दशरथात्मजम्","m":"Dasharatha's son"},{"d":"मानुषम्","m":"human"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"मन्ये","m":"thinking"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"यस्य","m":"from where"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"यश्च","m":"whence"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"भगवान्","m":"divine"},{"d":"मे","m":"me"},{"d":"ब्रवीतु","m":"tell"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"इतिब्रुवाणंकाकुत्स्थंब्रह्माब्रह्मविदांवरः अब्रवीच्छ्रुणुमेवाक्यंसत्यंसत्यपराक्रम ।","trans":"To Kakuthsa who spoke that way, creator Brahma replied, \"O Lord of truthful prowess, listen to my true submission.\"","words":[{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"ब्रुवाणम्","m":"having said"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थम्","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"ब्रह्मविदाम्","m":"creator, Brahma"},{"d":"वरः","m":"foremost"},{"d":"ब्रह्मा","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said"},{"d":"सत्यपराक्रम","m":"truthful prowess"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"सत्यम्","m":"truth"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"शृणु","m":"listen"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"भवान्नारायणोदेवःश्रीमांश्चक्रायुधःप्रभुः एकशृङ्गोवराहस्त्वंभूतभव्यसपत्नजित् ।","trans":"\"You are the divine self, glorious Narayana himself, wielder of discus. You are having a single tusk and a divine boar, knower of past and present.\"","words":[{"d":"भवान्","m":"yourself"},{"d":"देवः","m":"divine"},{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"glorious"},{"d":"चक्रायुधः","m":"wielder of discus"},{"d":"प्रभुः","m":"Lord"},{"d":"नाराणयः","m":"Narayana"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"एकशृङ्गः","m":"single tusk"},{"d":"वराहः","m":"boar"},{"d":"भूतभव्यसपत्नजित्","m":"knower of past and future"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"अक्षरंब्रह्मसत्यं च मध्येचान्ते च राघव लोकानांत्वंपरोधर्मोविष्वक्सेनश्चतुर्भुजः ।","trans":"\"You are the imperishable Brahma in the midst or end, abiding in truth. You are dharma, all pervading four shouldered Vishnu in the world.\"","words":[{"d":"अक्षरम्","m":"imperishable"},{"d":"मध्ये च","m":"in the midst"},{"d":"अन्ते च","m":"and end"},{"d":"सत्यं च","m":"truth"},{"d":"ब्रह्म","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"लोकानाम्","m":"in the world"},{"d":"धर्मः","m":"dharma"},{"d":"विष्वक्सेनः","m":"all pervading"},{"d":"चतुर्भुजः","m":"four shouldered"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"शार्ङ्गधन्वाहृषीकेशःपुरुषःपुरुषोत्तमः अजितःखङ्गदृग्विष्णुःकृष्णश्चैवमहाबलः ।","trans":"\"You are the wielder of Sarang bow, subduer of enemies, a supreme person, never faced defeat, wielder of sword, Vishnu, Krishna also and mighty.\"","words":[{"d":"शार्ङ्गधन्वा","m":"wielder of Saranga bow"},{"d":"हृषीकेशः","m":"subduer of senses"},{"d":"पुरुषः","m":"man"},{"d":"पुरुषोत्तमः","m":"supreme person"},{"d":"अजितः","m":"never faced defeat"},{"d":"खङ्गभृत्","m":"wielder of sword"},{"d":"विष्णुः","m":"Vishnu"},{"d":"कृष्णश्चैव","m":"Krishna also"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"सेनानीर्ग्रामणीश्चत्वंत्वंबुद्धिस्त्वंक्षमादमः प्रभवश्चाप्ययश्चत्वमुपेन्द्रोमधुसूदनः ।","trans":"\"You are the Karthikeya, the commander of army, village headman. You are the intellect, forbearance. You are the origin and end also. You are Vamana and destroyer of demon Madhu.\"","words":[{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सेनानीः","m":"commander of the army of gods (Karthikeya)"},{"d":"ग्रामणीश्च","m":"head of village"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"बुद्धिः","m":"intellect"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"क्षमा","m":"forbearance"},{"d":"दमः","m":"sense control"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"प्रभवः","m":"origin"},{"d":"अप्ययश्च","m":"and end"},{"d":"मधुसूदनः","m":"destroyer of demon Madhu"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"इन्द्रकर्मामहेन्द्रस्त्वंपद्मनाभोरणान्तकृत् शरण्यंशरणं च त्वामाहुर्दिव्यामहर्षयः ।","trans":"\"You are spoken of as the creator of Indra, Mahendra himself, Padmanabha, who puts an end to combat. You are a wonderful great sage and refuge of seekers.\"","words":[{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"इन्द्रकर्मा","m":"creator of Indra"},{"d":"महेन्द्रः","m":"Mahendra"},{"d":"पद्मनाभः","m":"Padmanabha, who has a lotus sprung from his navel"},{"d":"रणान्तकृत्","m":"who puts an end to combat"},{"d":"दिव्याः","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"शरण्यम्","m":"refuge"},{"d":"शरणम्","m":"of seekers"},{"d":"आहुः","m":"spoken of"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"सहस्रशृङ्गोवेदात्माशरशीर्षोमहर्षभः त्वंत्रयाणांहिलोकानामादिकर्तास्वयम्प्रभुः ।सिद्धानामपिसाध्यानामाश्रयश्चासिपूर्वजः","trans":"\"You are the self of Vedas with its thousand branches and hundred divisions. You are the beginning of the three worlds and end. You are the selfshining. You are the Siddha among the achievers and their refuge as well as their protector.\"","words":[{"d":"सहस्रशृङ्गः","m":"thousand branches"},{"d":"शतशीर्षः","m":"hundred divisions"},{"d":"महर्षभः","m":"great bull like"},{"d":"वेदात्मा","m":"self of Vedas"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"त्रयाणाम्","m":"three"},{"d":"लोकानाम्","m":"in worlds"},{"d":"आदिकर्ता","m":"beginning"},{"d":"स्वयम्प्रभुः","m":"selfshining"},{"d":"सिद्धानाम्","m":"Siddhas"},{"d":"साध्यानामपि","m":"among the achievers"},{"d":"पूर्वजः","m":"born first"},{"d":"आश्रयः च","m":"protector"},{"d":"असि","m":"you are"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"सहस्रशृङ्गोवेदात्माशरशीर्षोमहर्षभः त्वंत्रयाणांहिलोकानामादिकर्तास्वयम्प्रभुः ।सिद्धानामपिसाध्यानामाश्रयश्चासिपूर्वजः","trans":"\"You are the self of Vedas with its thousand branches and hundred divisions. You are the beginning of the three worlds and end. You are the selfshining. You are the Siddha among the achievers and their refuge as well as their protector.\"","words":[{"d":"सहस्रशृङ्ग