्रीमान्","m":"glorious"},{"d":"शतशीर्षः","m":"hundred heads"},{"d":"सहस्रदृक्","m":"with thousand eyes"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"भूतानि","m":"beings"},{"d":"सपर्वताम्","m":"all mountains"},{"d":"पृथिवीं","m":"earth च and"},{"d":"धारयसि","m":"sustain"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"अन्तेपृथिव्याःसलिलेदृश्यसेत्वंमहोरगः त्रीन्लोकान्धारयन् राम देवगन्धर्वदानवान् ।","trans":"\"Rama, at the dissolution of the earth you are seen to live on water and sustain a huge serpent. You are supporting the three worlds, the Devas, Gandharvas and Danavas.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"पृथिव्याः","m":"on earth"},{"d":"अन्ते","m":"end"},{"d":"सलिले","m":"in waters"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"त्रीन्","m":"three"},{"d":"लोकान्","m":"worlds"},{"d":"देवगन्धर्वदानवान्","m":"Devas, Gandharvas and Danavas"},{"d":"धारयन्","m":"sustain"},{"d":"महोरगः","m":"great serpent"},{"d":"दृश्यसे","m":"seen"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"अहंतेहृदयंरामजिह्वादेवीसरस्वती देवारोमाणिगात्रेषुब्रह्मणानिर्मिताःप्रभो ।","trans":"\"Rama, all gods constitute your heart, Devi Saraswathi is your tongue, the gods created by Brahma are the hair on your limbs.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"हृदयम्","m":"heart"},{"d":"देवी","m":"Devi"},{"d":"सरस्वती","m":"Saraswathi"},{"d":"जिह्वा","m":"tongue"},{"d":"प्रभो","m":"Lord"},{"d":"देवाः","m":"god"},{"d":"सर्वगात्रेषु","m":"limbs"},{"d":"रोमाणि","m":"hair"},{"d":"ब्रह्मणा","m":"by Brahma"},{"d":"निर्मिताः","m":"created"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"निमेषस्तेस्मृतारात्रिरुन्मेषोदिवसस्तथा संस्कारास्त्वभवन्वेदानैतदस्तित्वयाविना ।","trans":"\"When you close your eyelids, it becomes night and when you open it becomes day. Your perfection in action are the Vedas. Without you, there is nothing.\"","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"your"},{"d":"निमेषः","m":"closing your eyelids"},{"d":"रात्रिः","m":"night"},{"d":"स्मृता","m":"death"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"उन्मेषः","m":"open the eyelids"},{"d":"दिवसः","m":"day"},{"d":"संस्काराः","m":"perfection in a